org.apache.spark.scheduler

Class ResultDeletingTaskResultGetter

  • Object
    • org.apache.spark.scheduler.ResultDeletingTaskResultGetter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Logging

    public class ResultDeletingTaskResultGetter
extends Object
    Removes the TaskResult from the BlockManager before delegating to a normal TaskResultGetter.

    Used to test the case where a BlockManager evicts the task result (or dies) before the TaskResult is retrieved.
